==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: qīan lĭ yīn yúan yī xìan qīan

===Phrase===
'''[[千]][[里]][[姻缘]][[一线]][[牵]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') True love will remain, despite separation of great distances, even if by only a single thread.

